This directory has 2 sets of files:

init.pp & plugins.pp are clients.
server.pp & plugins.pp are used by servers.

It actually creates a full rabbitMQ server, with redis, and sets up SSL.


It follows the guide at: http://sensuapp.org/docs/0.12/guide

You'll need to create the certs by following the instructions at: http://sensuapp.org/docs/0.12/certificates


Oh: this uses the puppetlabs-rabbitmq.  It's actually capable of sharing a rabbitmq w/ mcollective.